                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A morlock can share the same space as another morlock, but no more than two morlocks can occupy the same space. When morlocks share the same space, they gain a +1 circumstance bonus to attack rolls.</p>\n<p>Vool can't use this ability if he's frightened (because the other morlock he could share a space with might be a vampire).</p>"
